  "description": "Set Team Card Image Container to Full Height\n\nConfigure the responsive-image-wrapper element within team-card-image components to occupy 100% of its parent container's height.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the responsive-image-wrapper element inside team-card-image components\n- Apply height: 100% CSS property to the responsive-image-wrapper\n- Ensure the parent container (team-card-image) has a defined height for percentage-based sizing to work\n- Verify images scale properly without distortion (maintain aspect ratio if needed)\n- Test across different viewport sizes to confirm responsive behavior\n- Check that the change doesn't break existing layout or cause overflow issues",
